"{\"uid\": \"rte.ie-kids-2024-0808-1464070-olympics-getting-to-know-sharlene-mawdsley-with-rtejr\", \"text\": \"  Tipp track star Sharlene Mawdsley was part of Team Ireland at the Paris Olympic Games. She is part of the Women's 4 x 400m Final relay team who have made the Final!  Before she said bon voyage, RT\\u00c9jr caught up with Sharlene to find out what things were like for her growing up in Newport, Co Tipperary. Press play above to find out about her school days and some of her fave things!  For more fun with Team Ireland check out onRT\\u00c9jr InstaandRT\\u00c9 Kids TikTok! We will have loads more content dropping and we will keep it going for the Paralympics too!!  For all the latest news check out Paris 2024 on RT\\u00c9.ie.    \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026. RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media. RT\\u00c9 is not responsible for the content of external internet sites.  Images Courtesy of Getty Images.\"}"